        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩具善巧方便及般若波羅蜜多清淨者，於諸法中若六塵境來為障礙，爾時應當如實覺了即是菩提。",
        "from": "T13n0400_014:0512b11_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "海意！",
        "from": "T13n0400_014:0512b11_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以是緣故，諸菩薩者應如是知。",
